      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "过马路时我一边走一边琢磨：要给她准备生日礼物，因为她快三十了；紧接着又转到求婚礼物和结婚的幻想里，却不知道到底送什么才合适。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_002",
      "target_id": "sent_002",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "念头接着往下滚：如果送她求婚礼物，我们好像就能顺理成章结婚，但我仍然卡在‘送什么’这个现实问题上。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_003",
      "target_id": "sent_003",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "她偏爱香奈儿那种昂贵符号，可我囊中羞涩，只能承认自己买不起。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_004",
      "target_id": "sent_004",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "走着走着瞥见书店，忽然觉得书也是一种体面又不那么招摇的礼物选项。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_005",
      "target_id": "sent_005",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "进店随手翻阅时，我先用书里夹玫瑰制造浪漫，又因玫瑰易凋而感到心碎；随即想象力跑偏到枪械坏人威胁自己，掺杂害怕与滑稽的自嘲。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_006",
      "target_id": "sent_006",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "接续上文惊魂未定式的联想：坏人埋伏书里拿枪瞄准，让我惴惴不安。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_007",
      "target_id": "sent_007",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "梦境般的打斗接续：对方开枪，我躲开，心里更多是恼火而不是真正的伤亡恐惧。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_008",
      "target_id": "sent_008",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "视线落到机票上，旅行的念头一下子冲淡先前阴影，我忍不住笑出来。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_009",
      "target_id": "sent_009",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "一想到婚后的蜜月旅行就更轻快，笑意几乎是自我安抚式的甜蜜想象。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_010",
      "target_id": "sent_010",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我把念头落实到行动：拿起手机给她发信息。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_011",
      "target_id": "sent_011",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我问她婚后想去哪蜜月；她用地标名胜列出向往清单，把浪漫写成一串世界符号。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_012",
      "target_id": "sent_012",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "电话打断思绪后，我在一堆名胜候选里漂浮，最后落到‘去美国’这个略显随意的终点。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_013",
      "target_id": "sent_013",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "美国的意象被快速枚举：政治地标、流行偶像与体育场并列，像旅行广告拼贴。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_014",
      "target_id": "sent_014",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "‘世贸中心’触发爆炸联想，惊讶来自记忆符号猛然闯入白日梦。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_015",
      "target_id": "sent_015",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我开始务实检索航班、机场、酒店与攻略，把幻想推进到伪行程层面。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
      "annotator_note": "在不改变信息的前提下用更口语、连贯的中文重述整句交际意图。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_ft_016",
      "target_id": "sent_016",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "攻略页面罗列星级酒店档次与文旅消费符号，奢华想象像菜单一样摊开。",
      "confidence": 0.86,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "Composer (GPT-5.2 via Cursor)",
